### List all Stripe payments (default: 20 most recent)
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments

### List Stripe payments filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments?status=succeeded

### List Stripe payments filtered by payment type
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments?payment_type=payment_intent

### List Stripe payments filtered by currency
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments?currency=EUR

### List Stripe payments filtered by card brand
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments?card_brand=visa

### List Stripe payments with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments?status=succeeded&currency=EUR&limit=5

### List Stripe payments with pagination (page 2)
GET http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments?limit=10&offset=10

### Simulate Stripe payments (from recent internal payments)
POST http://localhost:8000/stripe-payments/simulate
Content-Type: application/json
